_sText:
This is one of my first maps for CSS.

I don't have much experience in mapping but I wanted to try something different. And here is the result: I created some kind of mines and placed them all around the map. So it can be really difficult to kill each other.

Already one of this little things will kill you (and maybe the guy next to you :P) if you haven't an armor!


Please try it and write some comments.
